file.name: spec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  version: 0.1.0
  title: Test
  description: test
paths:
  /names:
    get:
      description: Get all names
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  data:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        id: { type: string }
                        name: { type: string }
                        lang: { type: string}
                        country: { type: string }
                        type: { type: string }
                  meta:
                    type: object
                    properties:
                      type: { type: string }
                      page: { type: integer }
                      limit: { type: integer }
                      total: { type: integer }
    post:
      description: Create name
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required: [name, lang, country, type]
              properties:
                name: { type: string }
                lang: { type: string}
                country: { type: string }
                type: { type: string }
      responses:
        201:
          description: CREATED
